Package: metro
Title: A Manhattan Plot Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Anastasia", "Lucas", email = "anastasia.lucas.bioinfo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package creates Manhattan plots for *ome-wide association studies. It is designed to improve on traditional Manhattan plots by incorporating additional information in a way that is both useful for interpretation and aesthetically pleasing. 
Depends: ggplot2
Suggests: gganimate, ggiraph, htmlwidgets, ggrepel, RColorBrewer
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
